narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I greatly developed my French skills, especially complex grammar, and I feel that I have become more competent in French and am able to write better.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I liked how the course gave us lots of practice with the course packets. Perhaps it would have been nice to do the exam during reading week like my friends in Spanish.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would recommend this course to another student if they wanted to advance their French skills.
